query: SELECT ig.id, ig.name as guide_name, COUNT(p.id) as matching_places FROM island_guides ig LEFT JOIN places p ON ig.name = p.name GROUP BY ig.id, ig.name HAVING matching_places = 0 ORDER BY ig.id LIMIT 20;
